ntact with intelligent EBEs might have more to teach us than a 2000 year old, Romanised, Jewish cult???<br><br>Just a few thoughts .. sorry if I've veered widely off the subject!<br><br>Paul<br>Powys/ UK <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/urhoadesb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>rhoadesb</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 124<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(7/19/01 3:36:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesufos.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=78.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Aliens: Angels or Demons</span><hr size=1> I'm not trying to say humans are wasps, however the following puts things in better perspective:<br><br>If a man wipes out a colony of wasps, is it an angelic, or a demonic act?<br><br>Another thread, on another ezboard, with similar thinking:<br><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub1.ezboard.com/ftheunexplainedforumgeneralunexplained.showMessage?topicID=315.topic">pub1.ezboard.com/ftheunex...=315.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <p>Bruce A. Rhoades</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/urhoadesb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>rhoadesb</A> at: 7/19/01 3:40:29 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#484848><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/upaulbst.showPublicProfile?language=EN>paulbst</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(7/20/01 1:22:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesufos.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=78.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Aliens: Angels or Demons</span><hr size=1> Hi Bruce, Dottie, Sunny, etc! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    I think Sunny expresses it really well - we need to have a degree of humility and perspective in considering how we might relate to living things from 'elsewhere'.<br><br>Who's to say that - in evolutionary, technological or other terms - we might be regarded by  extraterrestrials much in the way Bruce that the man in your analogy relates to 'wasps' <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     :  if this is the case, lets hope that 'they' have a rather more compassionate and inclusive sense of morality than we sometimes appear to have.<br><br>To answer your point directly Bruce: if the man in question had created the wasps, had placed them there in the first place, had given them their sting, and was 'omnipotent' &amp; all-powerful and could therefore equally choose to leave them alone, then YES - wiping them out would be a 'demonic' thing to do (as in my opinion was the flood, etc) ... just my opinion! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Anyway -- an interesting website I've found: it belongs to a Christian organisation called 'Alien Resistance', who believe that the alien abduction phenomena is actually a manifestation of DEMONIC intervention in human affairs, and who seek to actively resist this:<br>www.alienresistance.org/christianufo.htm <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>... I don't agree with them, but it's an interesting site none-the-less.<br><br>Actually Dottie, I've just realised, this link relates to your original post: the members of Alien Resistance believe that 'aliens' are a modern-day manifestation of the Nephilim - who you referred to originally ...<br><br>Paul<br>Powys/ UK<br><!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/upaulbst.showPublicProfile?language=EN>paulbst</A> at: 7/20/01 1:54:25 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/udotzap.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DOTZAP</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Angelight</span><br>  Posts: 2991<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(7/20/01 6:34:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesufos.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=78.topic&index=15>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/maidenntheshaden/maxmouse.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Aliens: Angels or Demons</span><hr size=1> Paulbst, I see our thoughts are very similar. I really enjoyed reading your posts. Thanks much. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Hi there Roadesb. Great link. Thanks! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>~~~Dottie~~~<br> <p><img src=http://photoasa.com/disk2/2737/49775_dottiehm.gif><br>"The love for all living creatures is the noblest attribute of man."<br>~~~Charles Darwin~~~<br>Please visit us at the <font size=3><a href="http://pub12.ezboard.com/bthoughtmessageboard">Thought Message Board</a><br><font size=1><a href="http://pub15.ezboard.com/btheguardianacademy">